MERGE [ReviewAnswers] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, 0),
(@p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 1),
(@p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, 2)) AS i ([Answer], [CreatedAt], [EmpNo], [Outlet], [PhotoFilePath], [QuestionId], [Rscode], [SelectedOptions], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Answer], [CreatedAt], [EmpNo], [Outlet], [PhotoFilePath], [QuestionId], [Rscode], [SelectedOptions])
VALUES (i.[Answer], i.[CreatedAt], i.[EmpNo], i.[Outlet], i.[PhotoFilePath], i.[QuestionId], i.[Rscode], i.[SelectedOptions])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[ReviewAnswerId], i._Position;
